*1999年12月6日晚上8時35分，T·F·格林機場的5R/23L跑道發生跑道入侵事件，涉及聯合航空1448號航班和聯邦快遞1662號航班<ref name="LAT">{{cite news|title=Planes Urged to Stop at Runway Intersections|url=http://www.sptimes.com/News/061400/Worldandnation/Planes_urged_to_stop_.shtml|newspaper=Los Angeles Times/St. Petersburg Times|date=2000-06-14|accessdate=2016-04-17|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065412/http://www.sptimes.com/News/061400/Worldandnation/Planes_urged_to_stop_.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後因全美航空2998號航班的機長發現而避免了意外。事後該機長獲全美航空表揚。而肇事的空中管制員和聯合航空機師則被停職作進一步培訓，其後獲復職<ref name="NTSB">{{cite news|title=Animations of runway incursions from Board Meeting of June 13, 2000|url=http://www.beta.ntsb.gov/Events/2000/incursion/incur_video.htm|publisher=National Transportation Safety Board|date=2000-06-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130218132327/http://www.beta.ntsb.gov/Events/2000/incursion/incur_video.htm|archivedate=2013-02-18|accessdate=2016-04-17}}</ref>。
*2007年12月16日，[[威斯康辛航空|威斯康辛航空]]3758號航班，在進場不穩的情況下在跑道5硬著陸，最後停在跑道左側<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ntsb.gov/aviationquery/brief.aspx?ev_id=20071217X01939&key=1|publisher=National Transportation Safety Board|title=Probable Cause, DCA08FA018|date=2008-12-30|accessdate=2011-06-07|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230235103/http://www.ntsb.gov/aviationquery/brief.aspx?ev_id=20071217X01939&key=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

